column5: Will be traveling through Fort Frances at approx 2:00 - 3:00 am on Saturday morning, the 17th.We will be driving 30 miles north ofEmo, and flying out at 7:00 am.What are the chances of liquor store being open at that time of the morning?
Slim and none. I'd contact the outfitter and arrange for someone to pick your beer up for you prior to your arrival.
